---
title: Pumpkin & Leek Risotto with Truffle Oil, Almond-Sage Topping & Plant-Based Parmesan
description: This rich pumpkin risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you to kick your feet up and enjoy quality time
with the ones who matter. With the luxurious addition of truffle oil, it takes this plant-based meal to the next
a level – taste it and see!

